    {
        "Key": "page1.4",
        "Speaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我驻足良久。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.5",
        "Speaker": "H克罗瑞娜",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你在看什么呢？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.6",
        "Speaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "克罗瑞娜突如其来的声音让我从思绪中回过神来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.7",
        "Speaker": "H主角",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你这幅画……画的究竟是什么？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.8",
        "Speaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "克罗瑞娜俏皮地笑了笑。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.9",
        "Speaker": "H克罗瑞娜",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你猜？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page1.10",
        "Speaker": "H克罗瑞娜",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "给你个小提示，这幅画是我特意定制的，可不是什么普通作品哦。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "choice01",
        "Speaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这是恐怖片现场？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "choice02",
        "Speaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这是抽象派脑洞？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page2.1",
        "Speaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page2.2",
        "Speaker": "H克罗瑞娜",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "当然不是啊。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page2.3",
        "Speaker": "H克罗瑞娜",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这是我家啦，吉诺拉庄园的风景写实画！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page2.4",
        "Speaker": "H克罗瑞娜",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "还记得庄园正门的样貌吗？这里是大门，下方是庭院……你应该都有去过的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page2.5",
        "Speaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我再次端详这张油画，似乎看出点儿轮廓来了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page2.6",
        "Speaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "——好像还真是吉诺拉庄园。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page2.7",
        "Speaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "只不过这氛围有股说不清道不明、与吉诺拉庄园大相径庭的诡异，再加之画匠的独特笔触，乍一看我居然真没看出来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page2.8",
        "Speaker": "H主角",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这颜色可真是……独特。",
        "disable": 0
